# Contributing

## Onboarding

- Node.js
- We use pnpm
- Clone
- `pnpm i`
- `pnpm astro dev`

## Writing

- Titles and headings are written in sentence case.
- Avoid introducing new usage of "whitelist" or "blacklist". Existing usage in aliases or command names are kept.
- Avoid using second person pronouns like "you".
- Use objective language.

## Media

- Use `.webp` or `.webm` for images and videos respectively.

### Text alternatives

Writing text alternatives is encouraged. Documents may be displayed in places which do not support images. A descriptive text alternative can be displayed in place of the image.
